    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Curvelicious</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curvelicious is a fast-paced, action-packed twist on classic curve and snake games, delivering intense multiplayer fun with strategic depth. Gather your friends for local multiplayer matches and enjoy endless excitement with multiple modes, power-ups, and customizable gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/1a316d133b318bd978be06bb66219b69.avif?t=1762016729\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras_big/1a316d133b318bd978be06bb66219b69.avif?t=1762016729 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <strong>Competitive Local Multiplayer Mayhem</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Curvelicious supports up to 8 players locally, with adjustable play area sizes to match the number of participants. Whether it's a small, intimate duel or an all-out 8-player brawl, the game scales to fit the action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/2ca0463e852bf17301604ab2be77926a.poster.avif?t=1762016729\" width=600 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/2ca0463e852bf17301604ab2be77926a.webm?t=1762016729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/2ca0463e852bf17301604ab2be77926a.mp4?t=1762016729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gamepad Support</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play comfortably with gamepad support for up to 8 players, ensuring a smooth and intuitive experience for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/9c165bf75f1ad9c08de6d36633147be6.avif?t=1762016729\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras_big/9c165bf75f1ad9c08de6d36633147be6.avif?t=1762016729 width=800 height=646 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>    Three Exciting Game Modes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      <i>  Arcade Mode: </i>The standard experience, featuring a variety of power-ups that keep the action unpredictable and fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >       <i> Custom Mode:</i> Take control! Adjust everything from curve width, speed, and choose which power-ups are available, letting you craft your own unique gameplay experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >      <i>  Classic Mode:</i> Go old school! No power-ups, just pure, skill-based curve mastery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dozens of Power-ups </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curvelicious features a wide variety of power-ups that radically change the gameplay.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use them strategically to gain an edge over your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/42d6608d70412250cdeec4a0514b7647.poster.avif?t=1762016729\" width=502 height=786 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/42d6608d70412250cdeec4a0514b7647.webm?t=1762016729\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244900/extras/42d6608d70412250cdeec4a0514b7647.mp4?t=1762016729\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Remote Play Together</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even if you’re not all in the same room, Steam’s Remote Play Together feature allows you to share the local multiplayer experience with your friends online.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Get Ready to Curve</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Curvelicious is all about quick reflexes, sharp strategies, and adaptable gameplay. Whether you're playing in Arcade Mode with chaotic power-ups, setting your own rules in Custom Mode, or going back to basics in Classic Mode, every match is a test of wits and skill.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to master the curves and outlast your competition? Gather your friends, set the rules, and dive into the curve-filled chaos today!</p>",
